1738
01:31:05.099 --> 01:31:07.068
[NAOMI GIGGLING]

1739
01:31:11.205 --> 01:31:12.640
-[SCREAMS IN EXCITEMENT]
-Oh!

1740
01:31:12.773 --> 01:31:13.741
